task.summary: 1. RS-tool project folder changed from Documents/RS-tool folder to %appdata%/RS-tool

1. Global refactoring. 2. Added new stat. plots for Adaboost, XGBoost, RandomForest. 3. Added 'Fixed random state' parameter. 4. Added dimensional reduction method selector. 5. Added 'Do Shapley' parameter. 6. Fixed multiple bugs.

1. Fixed critical bug during GridSearchCV parallel processing. - File "joblib\_memmapping_reducer.py", line 594 and 609, in register_folder_finalizer commented to avoid running program process copy. - 'with parallel_backend('multiprocessing', n_jobs=-1):' added to classificator functions 2. Minor bugs fixed.

v1.0.04 1) Added Recall-precision, F1-Score, accuracy GridSearchCV optimization. 2) Include x0 now refresh Deconvoluted dataset. 3) Fixed Voigt profile. 4) Fixed decomposition report bug with averaged metric. 5) Added new baseline correction method ExModPoly 6) Updated decomposition algorithm. 7) Fixed a lot of minor bugs. 8) Updated third party libraries.
v1.0.05 1) Added Pytorch neural net classifier. 2) Added ignore dataset's feature option. 3) Added LDA coeffitients equation to report. 4) Minor bug fixes and features.
